</h1>

<!-- intro slide three -->
<h1 class="big-text text-center" id="intro-3" style="display:none">In November 2013, SNAP households saw a cut in benefits after the 2009 American Recovery and Reinvestment Act's boost to the program ended. <br>
</h1>

<!-- intro slide four -->
<h1 class="big-text text-center" id="intro-4" style="display:none">Months later, the 2014 Farm Bill cut $8.7 billion from the program over the next ten years.<br>
</h1>

